OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CPlymouth's mayor referendum
OL,6,FA referendum will take place in
OL,7,FPlymouth in July to determine whether
OL,8,Fthe city should have a directly
OL,9,Felected mayor.
OL,11,FIt has been a divisive and bitter
OL,12,Fcampaign - and those in favour have
OL,13,Fthreatened to take the Government to
OL,14,Fcourt for 'betraying democracy'.
OL,16,FHere's a breakdown of everything you
OL,17,Fneed to know.
OL,19,FWhat is a directly elected mayor?
