OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CPlymouth's mayor referendum
OL,6,FA directly elected mayor is one of
OL,7,Fthree different 'political management
OL,8,Farrangements' available to local
OL,9,Fcouncils.
OL,11,FThe others are a leader and cabinet -
OL,12,Fwhich is currently how Plymouth
OL,13,Foperates - , and the 'committee
OL,14,Fsystem'.
OL,16,FDirectly elected mayors do not have
OL,17,Fadditional powers.
