OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CPlymouth's mayor referendum
OL,6,FEarlier this year, a petition was
OL,7,Fsigned by more than 13,000 people
OL,8,Fcalling for a referendum on whether
OL,9,FPlymouth should have a directly
OL,10,Felected mayor.
OL,12,FThe petition automatically triggered a
OL,13,Fvote, which will take place in the
OL,14,Fcity on Thursday, July 17th.
OL,16,FWho is leading the yes and no
OL,17,Fcampaigns?
OL,19,FThe 'Mayor for Plymouth' campaign is
OL,20,Fbeing led by Angus Forbes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
