OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CPlymouth's mayor referendum
OL,6,FMr Forbes is a businessman,
OL,7,Fentrepreneur and philanthropist who is
OL,8,Fmarried to Dame Darcey Bussell, a
OL,9,Fformer ballerina and television
OL,10,Fpersonality.
OL,12,FThe campaign also has the support of
OL,13,Fformer Olympic swimmer Sharron Davies.
OL,15,FMr Forbes says 'the citizens of
OL,16,FPlymouth are suffering' and that a
OL,17,Fdirectly elected mayor will improve
OL,18,Fthe city.
