OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CPlymouth's mayor referendum
OL,6,FThe opposing campaign is being
OL,7,Fspearheaded by Plymouth Labour
OL,8,Ffigures, including councillors Jemima
OL,9,FLaing and Charlotte Holloway.
OL,11,FThey have branded it a 'vanity
OL,12,Fproject' and say it is a waste of
OL,13,Fmoney.
OL,15,FWho would the new mayor be?
OL,17,FIt is not yet clear who the candidates
OL,18,Fmight be for a mayoral election.
