OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CPlymouth's mayor referendum
OL,6,FAngus Forbes says he would like "a
OL,7,Fwide range of candidates from across
OL,8,Fthe city" - he estimates that eight
OL,9,Fpeople, both men and women, may put
OL,10,Ftheir names forward.
OL,12,FMr Forbes says he will not be among
OL,13,Fthe candidates.
OL,15,FIs the Government scrapping directly
OL,16,Felected mayors?
