OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CPlymouth's mayor referendum
OL,6,FThe Government plans to introduce
OL,7,Flegislation which would stop the
OL,8,Fcreation of new city mayors, while
OL,9,Faccepting the continuation of 13
OL,10,Fexisting mayors.
OL,12,FIf Plymouth votes yes on July 17th,
OL,13,Fthe proposed first election will be
OL,14,Fdelayed until 2027 while the
OL,15,Flegislation goes through Parliament.
OL,17,FBut Angus Forbes has responded to this
OL,18,Fby threatening to take the Government
OL,19,Fto court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
