OL,3,CEverything you need to know about
OL,4,CPlymouth's mayor referendum
OL,6,FHe accused Ministers of 'betraying
OL,7,Fdemocracy and the citizens of
OL,8,FPlymouth', adding: 'Plymothians want
OL,9,Fchange, they want better democracy,
OL,10,Fthey want their voice to be heard.
OL,12,F"If the Government tries to stop us on
OL,13,Fthe grounds of some prospective
OL,14,Flegislation, we will see them in the
OL,15,FHigh Court where we will win."
